        <item>
            <title>赛车游戏《Test Drive Unlimited》相隔 12 年推新作回归，以香港岛做主题、超逼真还原街景</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/tdusc-hk/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=tdusc-hk</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/tdusc-hk/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 12:30:51 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[赛车]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1239519</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">由 KT Gaming 制作的赛车游戏 Test Drive Unlimited 系列继 12 年前的 Test Drive: Ferrari Racing Legends 后，终于推出新作 Test Drive Unlimited Solar Crown（TDUSC）。本次新作将赛车舞台搬到香港岛，是系列首次将背景放在亚洲。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1239530" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ss_ee5f1c1466411cd25-694x390.jpg" alt="Test Drive Unlimited Solar Crown" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ss_ee5f1c1466411cd25-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ss_ee5f1c1466411cd25.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1239531 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ss_f434b3987297b6bd0-1-694x390.jpg" alt="Test Drive Unlimited Solar Crown" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ss_f434b3987297b6bd0-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ss_f434b3987297b6bd0-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1239532 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ss_37420489a7069c1f2-694x390.jpg" alt="Test Drive Unlimited Solar Crown" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ss_37420489a7069c1f2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/ss_37420489a7069c1f2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1249970/Test_Drive_Unlimited_Solar_Crown/">Steam</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">游戏发行商 Nacon 公布的预告片中，可以看到在香港岛不同角落赛车的片段，逼真还原了香港岛的街头景观。TDUSC 以一个极具影响力的神秘组织做背景，他们四处邀请会员参加赛车，为追求崇高的声望和对赛车的热爱而不断竞赛。玩家可以在游戏中自由探索香港岛，参与当地的竞赛并使用自己改装的赛车称霸「Solar Crown」赛事。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1239524 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire-1717144566-536x580.jpg" alt="TDUSC" width="536" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire-1717144566-536x580.jpg 536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire-1717144566.jpg 831w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 536px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1249970/Test_Drive_Unlimited_Solar_Crown/">Steam</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Test Drive Unlimited Solar Crown 将会于 9 月 12 日登陆 PC、PS5 与 Xbox Series X/S 平台。目前 Steam 上预购价为 $308，「Silver Sharps」和「Silver Streets」两个 DLC 同捆包则为 $469，亦有推出 $556 的豪华版，除了包含上述 DLC 的内容之外更可以提早 7 天游玩游戏。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8GUCrMPJgkE">PlayStation</a>、<a href="https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=264451">巴哈姆特</a></p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8GUCrMPJgkE">PlayStation</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/27/%e3%80%90%e8%a9%95%e6%b8%ac%e3%80%91ps5%e3%80%8a%e6%b5%aa%e4%ba%ba%e5%b4%9b%e8%b5%b7%e3%80%8b%e3%80%80%e5%b9%95%e6%9c%ab%e4%ba%82%e4%b8%96%e6%b4%bb%e5%87%ba%e8%87%aa%e7%94%b1/game-channel/game-review/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】PS5《浪人崛起》　幕末乱世活出自由</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/gow5-on-pc/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">《战神：诸神黄昏》9 月登陆 PC　需要用 PSN 帐号登入才可玩</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/monsterhunterwilds/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Monster Hunter Wilds 首段预告片【有片睇】新魔物 + 新坐骑 + 新玩法</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/tdusc-hk/game-channel/">赛车游戏《Test Drive Unlimited》相隔 12 年推新作回归，以香港岛做主题、超逼真还原街景</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
