        </item>
        <item>
            <title>长城欧拉 ORA 07 登陆香港　「一换一」售价 239,900 起</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/ora-07-hk/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ora-07-hk</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/ora-07-hk/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 12:15:36 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Ora]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[电动车]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1239588</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近年在香港中国品牌电动车选择越来越多，最近长城汽车旗下的 ORA（欧拉）继之前的 03 后，正式推出 ORA 07 四门跑房车系列，「一换一」售价由 239,900 起。今日这部超流线型 4 门纯电轿跑车 ORA 07 就率先登陆将军澳宝林 <span lang="EN-US">MCP CENTRAL </span>展出。小编就到现场同大家率先睇这部刚刚来港的新电动车。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239618" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_152846-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_152846-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_152846.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239619" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_152930-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_152930-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_152930.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span id="more-1239588"></span></p><p>ORA 07 本身在中国名为「闪电猫」，外观和车厢设计也一贯品牌其他车款的圆润风格，类似宾利 Continental GT，尺寸为 4,874 x 1,850 x 1,500mm，轴距则为 2,870mm。登陆香港的 ORA 07 有三个版本，包括标准前驱版本（续航距离 440 公里）、长续航前驱版本（续航距离 570 公里），以及四驱 GT 版本（续航距离 520 公里），三个版本的「一换一」售价分别为 HK$239,000 起、HK$269,000 起和 HK$329,000 起。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239636" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153949-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153949-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153949-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239620" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153544-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153544-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153544.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239621" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153549-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153549-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153549.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239622" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153606-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153606-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153606-rotated.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239623" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153626-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153626-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153626.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>ORA 07 采超流线型车身和无框车窗设计，提升视觉美感之余，更将行车风阻系数降至 0.22cd，让行车效能大大提高，每次充电后行驶距离也得到延长。</p><p>内笼设计同样令人惊艳，车厢采用全球首次引入的空调紫外线杀菌灯，为驾驶者与乘客提供洁净空气。前后座位皆以仿真皮革包覆，搭配亮眼橙色内饰，既展现活力又不失优雅。挡风玻璃以及前座车窗采用减音材料制成，提供更宁静的车厢环境。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239624" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153727-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153727-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153727.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239628" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153824-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153824-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153824.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239626" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153653-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153653-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153653-rotated.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239627" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_1537190-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_1537190-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_1537190.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239633" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/img_1035-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/img_1035-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/img_1035.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>ORA 07 配备了多项先进科技系统，包括自动调节进气格栅，能够根据外界气温自动开合，确保摩打在最佳环境下运行。同时，车辆搭载四轮驱动系统，提供稳定的驾驶体验。电池容量达 83 kWh，最大续航距离可达 520 公里，让驾驶者无需频繁充电即可轻松出行。动力方面，标准前驱版本和长续航前驱版本马力有 204ps、扭力 340Nm，0 至 100 km/h 加速时间为 7.9 秒，而四驱 GT 版本则采用双摩打四驱，马力达到 408ps、扭力 680Nm，0 至 100km/h 加速时间为 4.3 秒。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239629" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153835-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153835-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531_153835.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239634" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/img_10242-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/img_10242-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/img_10242.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>行车安全方面，全车以 77.6% 高强度材质制作，并配有 L2 智能驾驶辅助系统，包括「ACC」主动式车距调节巡航系统及「ICC」智能巡航控制。车辆前方装有行车镜头、12 个超声波感应器和 2 个毫米波雷达，为驾驶者及乘客提供全方位的安全保障。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239631" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/img_10302-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/img_10302-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/img_10302.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239632" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/img_1023-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/img_1023-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/img_1023.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><strong>ORA 07 车款详细规格</strong></p><ul><li>电池容量：83 kWh</li><li>最大续航距离：520 公里（WLTP combine）</li><li>最大功率：300 kW</li><li>最大扭力：680 Nm</li><li>车身尺寸：4,874 x 1,850 x 1,500 mm</li></ul><ul><li>价格（一换一意向价）：
<ul><li>ORA 07 Standard Range：HKD $239,900</li><li>ORA 07 Long Range：HKD $269,900</li><li>ORA AWD GT：HKD $329,800</li></ul></li></ul><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239599" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240531at-2-501x580.jpg" alt="" width="501" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240531at-2-501x580.jpg 501w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240531at-2-scaled.jpg 777w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 501px" /></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/06/onvo-l60-from-nio-ev/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">蔚来子品牌 ONVO 电动车，将于月中发表支援换电</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/25/polestar-phone-launched/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Polestar Phone 发表，暂时只对应 Polestar 4 电动车</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/07/made-in-china-kia-ev5-international-version/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">中国制 KIA EV5 电动车，国际版率先出口泰国澳洲</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/ora-07-hk/life-tech/auto/">长城欧拉 ORA 07 登陆香港　「一换一」售价 239,900 起</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
