            <title>《战神：诸神黄昏》9 月登陆 PC　需要用 PSN 帐号登入才可玩</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/gow5-on-pc/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=gow5-on-pc</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/gow5-on-pc/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 09:00:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[战神，诸神黄昏]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1239495</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">PlayStation 于其官方节目「State of Play」中宣布《战神：诸神黄昏》（God of War Ragnarök）将会于 9 月 19 日登陆 PC 平台，但需要使用 PSN（PlayStation Network）的帐号登入后才能游玩。目前已于 Steam 和 Epic Game Store 开放预购，并会要求连结至 PSN 帐号。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1239506" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758742049_986a0ed3-694x390.jpg" alt="God of War Ragnarök" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758742049_986a0ed3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758742049_986a0ed3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://blog.playstation.com/2024/05/30/god-of-war-ragnarok-is-coming-to-pc/">PlayStation.Blog</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">《战神：诸神黄昏》PC 版将支援 4K 解析度，整合 NVIDIA RTX 深度学习超高采样（DLSS）技术、AMD FidelityFX 超级解析度（FSR），以及 Intel XeSS（Xe 超高采样）等，无上限帧率而且支援 21:9 和 32:9 的超寛萤幕模式。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1239504" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758825510_ed8d58a6-694x390.jpg" alt="God of War Ragnarök" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758825510_ed8d58a6-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758825510_ed8d58a6.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://blog.playstation.com/2024/05/30/god-of-war-ragnarok-is-coming-to-pc/">PlayStation.Blog</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">目前于 9 月 19 日前预购《战神：诸神黄昏》，可以得到克雷多斯苏雪盔甲、阿特柔斯苏雪束腰上衣（外观）的预购特典，两者均可在推进游戏剧情期间获得。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1239505" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758825500_1ec2a8b4-694x390.jpg" alt="God of War Ragnarök" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758825500_1ec2a8b4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/53758825500_1ec2a8b4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://blog.playstation.com/2024/05/30/god-of-war-ragnarok-is-coming-to-pc/">PlayStation.Blog</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">预购亦有推出豪华版，收录克雷多斯黑谷盔甲、阿特柔斯黑谷服装（外观）、混沌双刀用黑谷双刀手柄、利维坦之斧用黑谷斧柄、官方《战神：诸神黄昏》数位原声带和 Dark Horse 迷你数位美术集。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料来源：<a href="https://blog.playstation.com/2024/05/30/god-of-war-ragnarok-is-coming-to-pc/">PlayStation.Blog</a></p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m-4ZM3jxhdE&amp;t=763s">PlayStation</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/27/%e3%80%90%e8%a9%95%e6%b8%ac%e3%80%91ps5%e3%80%8a%e6%b5%aa%e4%ba%ba%e5%b4%9b%e8%b5%b7%e3%80%8b%e3%80%80%e5%b9%95%e6%9c%ab%e4%ba%82%e4%b8%96%e6%b4%bb%e5%87%ba%e8%87%aa%e7%94%b1/game-channel/game-review/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】PS5《浪人崛起》　幕末乱世活出自由</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/tdusc-hk/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">赛车游戏《Test Drive Unlimited》相隔 12 年推新作回归，以香港岛做主题、超逼真还原街景</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/monsterhunterwilds/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Monster Hunter Wilds 首段预告片【有片睇】新魔物 + 新坐骑 + 新玩法</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/gow5-on-pc/game-channel/">《战神：诸神黄昏》9 月登陆 PC　需要用 PSN 帐号登入才可玩</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
